staticFeed.text: Dilan Swain changed the location on IT'S TIME. This will now shoot in Los Angeles.
Matt Wilson added the roles of "Carly" and "Fred" to DOWNTOWN THUNDER.
Raylin Sabo changed the shoot dates for VIOLET ROAD. This will now shoot June through August 2018.
Mary Vernieu added the role of "Jenn" and "Timothy" to FAST TRACK.
Sam Shelley shared IT'S TIME to four clients.
